(1, 'Lecsó', '<p>A hagym&aacute;t apr&oacute;ra v&aacute;gjuk, &eacute;s olajon &uuml;vegesre pir&iacute;tjuk...</p>', 'főétel, vegetáriánus', 'https://minimalistbaker.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/EASY-Ratatouille-Versatile-1-Pot-Flavorful-French-inspired-packed-with-summer-vegetables-and-just-10-ingredients-required-minimalistbaker-recipe-plantbased-glutenfree-ratatouille-summer-4.jpg', 0),
